</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="36.[189,1398,700,762]" pageId="36" pageNumber="37">The specific name is a patronym in honor of the Cuban arachnologist Alexandre Sánchez-Ruiz for his contributions to the taxonomy of spiders.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
